.Sh NAME
.Nm varnishd
.Nd HTTP accelerator daemon
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Oo Fl a Ar address Ns
.Op : Ns Ar port
.Oc
.Oo Fl b Ar host Ns
.Op : Ns Ar port
.Oc
.Op Fl d
.Op Fl F
